P1.34 Lightsail Provider Implementation

## Summary
Implemented automatic backend selection between AWS Lightsail ($7-25/mo) and ECS Fargate ($65+/mo). Lightsail is auto-selected for simple apps based on workload signals.

## Backend Selection Logic
- Lightsail preferred for:
  * ≤500 expected users
  * No auto-scaling required
  * No production/enterprise keywords in description
- ECS Fargate preferred for:
  * >500 expected users
  * Auto-scaling required (maxCount > minCount)
  * Production keywords: 'production', 'prod', 'enterprise', 'high-availability', 'ha', 'mission-critical'

## Lightsail Power Levels
- Nano: 0.25 vCPU, 512MB @ $7/mo (≤50 users)
- Micro: 0.5 vCPU, 1GB @ $10/mo (≤200 users)
- Small: 1 vCPU, 2GB @ $25/mo (≤500 users)
- Medium/Large/XLarge for higher tiers

